reviewText: I haven't watched them all but I like what I have seen
Movie is kind of lame,  not the best looking characters and scenes.  Not your typical partiers and role players, Not recommended.

It met its goal as a demonstration of the concept of swinging. Not ALL of the couples
really entered into the spirit of swinging, although everyone agreed to do it.  Only parts
of two couples REALLY were into the swinging/exchanging.  The title of the was a little
bit of hoopla, but the reality was only two couples did any swinging.

A classy, professional DVD that is packed with information and insight. Highly recommended for couples interested in exploring the lifestyle/swinging world. Nothing like what I expected, this is an honest real-life look at an alternative lifestyle that can certainly be fun! I wasn't sure what to expect when I first watched this movie but I was both pleasantly surprised and aroused.  You will not be sorry you bought this.
